    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great with only minor signs of road use, and the interior remains clean and comfortable. Mechanically, it's solid and drives smoothly, making it a reliable choice for any buyer looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
