    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being offered strictly as-is for parts or a major restoration project. The body exhibits significant structural rust, particularly on the frame and floorboards, and the exterior paint has failed across all major panels. Mechanically, the car is currently non-running due to a suspected head gasket failure and a drained battery. The interior has seen better days, with numerous tears in the upholstery and a missing headliner.",
